@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
title Domain Model Excerpt â€“ Incident Type Catalog

class IncidentType <<Aggregate Root>> {
  +code: IncidentTypeCode
  +name: string
  +description: string
  +severity: Severity
  +parentCode: IncidentTypeCode?  ' nullable for root nodes
}

class IncidentTypeCode <<Value Object>> {
  +value: string  ' e.g., T-INC001
}

enum Severity {
  Minor
  Major
  Critical
}

IncidentType "0..*" --> "0..1" IncidentType : parentCode

IncidentType --> IncidentTypeCode
IncidentType --> Severity

note right of IncidentType
- code is unique and immutable
- parentCode must reference existing IncidentType (if set)
- cycles are forbidden
end note

@enduml